title: added missing arg and improved example clarity
body_html: The previous example was unclear because the output had 32 classes, but the target had only 4 classes. There was also inconsistencies between what the comments were saying versus what was happening. I added variables to hopefully clear some of these things up, and I also added the arg doc for a missing parameter.
